description: How to tile around unsquare walls…I used a T-Bevel against my level to find the angle. Then I cut the tile using my grinder. The tile has an expansion joint against the wall and remains even with the rest of the tile floor 🙌🏽🔥#tile #floor #homerenovation #oldhomes
title: How to Tile Around Unsquare Walls - #shorts #homerepairtutor
